paper_metadata.extraction_summary: Extracted genetic variant information for the KCNH2 gene, including penetrance data.

individual_records.evidence_sentence: Two novel pathogenic null variants were detected. KCNH2 c.2682_2685dup p.(Asp896Hisfs*25) is located in the 3′ end of exon 11 and within a few base pairs reach of 3 other frameshift variants previously reported in patients with LQTS.

functional_data.summary: The variant is a frameshift mutation leading to a premature stop codon.

variants.evidence_level: Strong evidence due to previous reports and functional implications.
variants.additional_notes: This variant is associated with long-QT syndrome and is located near other known pathogenic variants.
key_quotes: Two novel pathogenic null variants were detected. KCNH2 c.2682_2685dup p.(Asp896Hisfs*25) is located in the 3′ end of exon 11 and within a few base pairs reach of 3 other frameshift variants previously reported in patients with LQTS.
